          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm" data-i18n="sabaos.features.memory.desc">Persistent semantic memory across sessions. Engram graph database + Hindsight auto-recall. Agents don't forget.</p>
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card variant="elevated" hover>
        <div class="p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔒</div>
