          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm" data-i18n="sabaos.features.security.desc">Every code change passes through Security agent before merge. OWASP Top 10, SLSA L1, supply chain verification.</p>
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card variant="elevated" hover>
        <div class="p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔄</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-50 mb-3" data-i18n="sabaos.features.loop.title">Feedback Loop</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm" data-i18n="sabaos.features.loop.desc">Every task output feeds back into Engram. Continuous improvement baked into the architecture.</p>
