            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-400"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-brand mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg><span>Workflow automation</span></li>
